name: Lego Jurassic World : Legend of Isla Nublar
original_name: Lego Jurassic World : Legend of Isla Nublar
overview: Set in 2012, three years before the Jurassic World movie, Owen Grady and Claire Dearing team up on Isla Nublar to deal with everything the Jurassic World park throws their way, including a mysterious saboteur who wants to destroy the park forever!

episodes.name: Mission: Critical!
episodes.overview: Owen and Claire must rescue a theme-park reviewer from a sabotaged aerialtram… and a salivating T-Rex!

episodes.name: Stampede!
episodes.overview: While stranded in the jungle during a massive storm, Claire and Simon unknowingly stumble upon a clue to the whereabouts of the treasure sought by Sinjin.

episodes.name: The Hybrid Horror!
episodes.overview: A terrified hybrid dinosaur rampages through the park, causing chaos and creating cover for Danny and Sinjin as they try to steal the Nedry videotape!

episodes.name: Pteranodon't!
episodes.overview: A young park guest accidentally strands himself in the Pteranodon aviary, requiring Owen and a testy Stygimoloch to stage a daring rescue.

episodes.name: The Power and the Peril!
episodes.overview: Rock star mathematician Ian Malcolm returns to Isla Nublar and helps Claire, Owen and Hudson deal with strange power surges all over Jurassic World.

episodes.name: Spit Take!
episodes.overview: A Dilophosaurus runs loose in the park's hotel, and Owen and Claire must find it before the guests notice… and before Vic's dino-hunting security team can damage the hotel and the guests!

episodes.name: A Fish Story
episodes.overview: Vic and Owen find themselves, along with Sinjin, in the middle of a massive dino-fight in the old Jurassic Park Visitor Center!

episodes.name: Blown Away!
episodes.overview: It's déjà vu for Alan Grant as he returns to Isla Nublar and winds up stranded in the jungle during a dangerous storm with injured Simon and hero-worshipping Owen!

episodes.name: Haunted and Hunted!
episodes.overview: Something mysterious lurking the jungle wrecks a construction site, and Hudson is convinced a ghost is responsible… but it might be something even more surprising.

episodes.name: To the Extreme!
episodes.overview: Danny releases an energy drink into the dinosaurs' water supply, making them extra-energetic… and extra dangerous!

episodes.name: Symptoms!
episodes.overview: Owen falls prey to the toxin of a poisonous prehistoric jungle flower and believes he's a raptor!

episodes.name: Under the Volcano!
episodes.overview: Danny dons powerful dino-mech armor to dig up Cap'n No-Beard's treasure beneath Mt. Sibo, making him more than a match for our heroes… and a mighty allosaurus that unexpectedly joins the party!

episodes.name: The Monsters and the Mech!
episodes.overview: Hudson desperately recruits powerful help to defeat Danny once and for all… in the form of the T-Rex!
